      <title>美国 10 年期国债拍卖收益率一年来首次跌至 4% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-eyes-sub-4-yield-at-10-year-auction-for-first-time-in-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美联储将迅速大幅降息的预期推动，美国债券市场近日出现上涨，美国准备以一年来首次低于 4% 的收益率出售 10 年期美国国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/us-eyes-sub-4-yield-at-10-year-auction-for-first-time-in-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂芬·努钦表示是时候取消他创建的新国债了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/mnuchin-says-it-s-time-to-kill-the-new-treasury-bond-he-created</link>
      <description><![CDATA[只需快速浏览一下美国债券曲线，就能发现有些不对劲。有一种美国国债——20 年期国债——与市场其他部分脱节。它的收益率远高于其周边债券——10 年期和 30 年期国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/mnuchin-says-it-s-time-to-kill-the-new-treasury-bond-he-created</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
